          "name": "Elena Gryaznova",
          "email": "elena.gryaznova@seagate.com",
          "date": "2016-10-05 13:48:08.000000000",
          "tz": 180
        },
        "subject": "LU-2525 tests: specify the set of tests to be run",
        "message": "LU-2525 tests: specify the set of tests to be run\n\n1) flock test_1a() executes all tests keep in TEST_DIR_LTP_FLOCK,\nit is reasonable to reduce the tests set to the number of tests\nrelated to nfs flock;\n2) no reason to continue LTP tests after first failure occurs,\nexit with error if any;\n3) SINGLECLIENT could be empty, set it to HOSTNAME in this case;\n4) remove wrong EXPORT_OPTS value; test requires no_root_squash\nset by t-f by default;\n5) customize NFS_MNT and LUSTRE_MNT.\n\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-3620\nSigned-off-by: Elena Gryaznova <elena.gryaznova@seagate.com>\nReviewed-by: Alexander Lezhoev <alexander.lezhoev@seagate.com>\nReviewed-by: Andriy Skulysh <andriy.skulysh@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: Iea1b7c5004603fcf7730f0c8a26a26d050eed32f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
